      },
      {
        "start": "03:34.600",
        "end": "03:36.500",
        "original": "あずき先輩、ゴー！",
        "english": "AZKi-senpai, go!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:37.200",
        "end": "03:38.500",
        "original": "え、何？",
        "english": "Eh, what?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:40.500",
        "end": "03:42.500",
        "original": "何か濡れてる、濡れてる",
        "english": "It's wet, it's wet.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:42.600",
        "end": "03:44.200",
        "original": "やっぱ濡れてるんだ",
        "english": "So it is wet.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:44.300",
        "end": "03:47.500",
        "original": "え、何か、湿って、湿っています",
        "english": "Eh, it's kind of... damp, it's damp.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:47.800",
        "end": "03:49.500",
        "original": "湿っている、湿度高めなんだこれ",
        "english": "Damp... the humidity is high for this one.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:49.600",
        "end": "03:50.500",
        "original": "どういうこと？",
        "english": "What does that mean?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:50.600",
        "end": "03:54.000",
        "original": "え、何この、トゲトゲした球体のような",
        "english": "Eh, what is this... like a prickly sphere?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:54.500",
        "end": "03:58.500",
        "original": "球体？球体と、その下にもトゲトゲしたものが",
        "english": "A sphere? A sphere, and there are prickly things below it too.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:59.000",
        "end": "04:00.500",
        "original": "トゲトゲがいっぱいあるってこと？",
        "english": "So there are many prickly things?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:00.800",
        "end": "04:02.500",
        "original": "痛くはないけど",
        "english": "It doesn't hurt, but...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:02.600",
        "end": "04:03.500",
        "original": "痛くはない？",
        "english": "It doesn't hurt?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:03.600",
        "end": "04:06.500",
        "original": "え、これ何だ？何なんだろう",
        "english": "Eh, what is this? I wonder what it is.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:06.600",
        "end": "04:07.400",
        "original": "何、何、わかんない",
        "english": "What, what? I don't know.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:08.600",
        "end": "04:10.000",
        "original": "めっちゃむずいんだ、じゃ",
        "english": "It's super hard then.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:10.100",
        "end": "04:12.800",
        "original": "何だこれー！",
        "english": "What is this?!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:13.000",
        "end": "04:15.500",
        "original": "なんか湿ってる",
        "english": "It's kind of damp.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:15.600",
        "end": "04:19.500",
        "original": "みおちゃんですかね、次。最後ゼタに決めてもらう",
        "english": "I guess Mio-chan is next. Finally, we'll have Zeta decide.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:19.600",
        "end": "04:24.000",
        "original": "優しい、優しい、何か嫌だなその感想聞いた状態でやる、触るのちょっと嫌だかも",
        "english": "Kind, kind? I don't like doing it after hearing that impression. Touching it might be a bit unpleasant.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:27.100",
        "end": "04:28.500",
        "original": "ゴー！",
        "english": "Go!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:28.600",
        "end": "04:31.500",
        "original": "嫌だな、濡れてるって前情報で嫌だ",
        "english": "I hate this. Knowing it's wet beforehand is the worst.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:31.600",
        "end": "04:33.200",
        "original": "濡れてる？",
        "english": "Is it wet?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:33.500",
        "end": "04:36.500",
        "original": "うわー、やっぱ濡れてるなー",
        "english": "Whoa, it really is wet.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:36.600",
        "end": "04:37.500",
        "original": "濡れてる？",
        "english": "Wet?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:37.600",
        "end": "04:40.500",
        "original": "おおー、濡れてる",
        "english": "Oh, it's wet.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:40.800",
        "end": "04:46.500",
        "original": "けど、濡れてるけど、何か固くて、確実にたくさんいる",
        "english": "But, it's wet, but it's kind of hard... and there are definitely a lot of them.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:46.600",
        "end": "04:51.500",
        "original": "たくさんいる？たくさんいるぞ、一体何なんだよ",
        "english": "A lot of them? There's a lot! What on earth are they?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:51.600",
        "end": "04:53.500",
        "original": "これ、なんだ？",
        "english": "What is this?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:53.600",
        "end": "04:58.500",
        "original": "え、でもこれあんまり見かけないやつの気がする",
        "english": "Eh, but I feel like this isn't something I see often.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:58.600",
        "end": "05:00.500",
        "original": "見かけない？",
        "english": "Not something you see often?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      }
    ],
    "model_name": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
  }
